I personally like to make a copy of the original ROM and to apply the patch to the duplicate.  This way, I can have both the original and the patch and can select between them easily in the Open dialog.<br /><br />That's my taste, though, and I fully respect those who prefer soft patching.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=360">dvdmth</a> — Sat Apr 21, 2007 10:41 am</p><hr />
